The Festa Academy festival offers for the third time festivals that connect the International Student Day with the anniversary of the Velvet Revolution with a musical part.
During the festival there are 20 choirs from upper and secondary schools.
The festival's nail consists of two concerts organized on 17 November.
Charles University has an important part in this festival.
